Important sections for implementation:

 * URI - [rfc7230] Section 2.7
 * URI forms - [rfc7230] Section 5.3
   ::: origin-form, absolute-form, authority-form, asterisk-form
 * Effective URI - [rfc7230] Section 5.5
   ::: converting from relative to absolute path?

NOTE: HTTP separates
      __resource identification__ (URI) from
      __request semantics__ (request method + request-modifying headers).

